[*] --> Shipped
Shipped --> Cancelled : approve
Cancelled --> Rejected : process
Cancelled : entry / log service
Rejected --> Active : reject
Active --> OnHold : process
OnHold --> Created : submit
OnHold : entry / log service
OnHold --> Created : revert
Created --> [*]
